<lb n="0217b04"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0217b05"/>
<lb n="0217b06"/><head type="no">No. 1089</head>
<lb n="0217b07"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0217001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】享和年間刊豐山大學藏本，【甲】平安時代寫東寺三密藏本</note>都表如意摩尼轉輪聖王次第念
<lb n="0217b08"/>誦祕密最要略法</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0217b09"/>
<lb n="0217b10"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0217002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔解脫師子譯〕－【甲】</note><app n="0217002"><lem>解脫師子譯</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0217b11"/><div1 type="pin"><mulu type="品" level="1" n="1" label="1 相貌品"/><head>相貌品第一</head>
<lb n="0217b12"/><lg><l>我今當說思惟<note n="0217003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">法＝寶&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0217003" corr="寶" resp="【原】">法</sic></l><l>三種真言而次第</l>
<lb n="0217b13"/><l>初用大心外加持</l><l>第二根本復想內</l>
<lb n="0217b14"/><l>第三小心內外通</l><l>應可存心無錯亂</l>
<lb n="0217b15"/><l>如是三道妙真言</l><l>安立行者明王地</l>
<lb n="0217b16"/><l>若有修此三昧耶</l><l>須具七種殊勝相</l>
<lb n="0217b17"/><l>猶如輪王持七寶</l><l>王四天下皆降伏</l>
<lb n="0217b18"/><l>次說順諸念誦法</l><l>復擇<note n="0217004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">清淨吉祥＝淨吉祥之【甲】</note><app n="0217004"><lem>清淨吉祥</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">淨吉祥之</rdg></app>地</l>
<lb n="0217b19"/><l>或在山間及池邊</l><l>或在伽藍精室處</l>
<lb n="0217b20"/><l>或<note n="0217005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">佛＝神&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0217005"><lem>佛</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">神</rdg></app>舍利神塔中</l><l>應可存心辦諸俱</l>
<lb n="0217b21"/><l>先以持地如教命</l><l><note n="0217006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">復次＝次復【甲】</note><app n="0217006"><lem>復次</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">次復</rdg></app>安置本尊者</l>
<lb n="0217b22"/><l>行者自須敷已座</l><l>尊面西方在目前</l>
<lb n="0217b23"/><l>行者像前面東坐</l><l>清淨沐浴香塗身</l>
<lb n="0217b24"/><l>兼著新淨妙衣服</l><l>又持種種供養具</l>
<lb n="0217b25"/><l>步步想<note n="0217007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">八＝成【甲】</note><app n="0217007"><lem>八</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">成</rdg></app>葉蓮華</l><l>存想變地無濁穢</l>
<lb n="0217b26"/><l>加持護身入精室</l><l>安置像前而念誦</l></lg></div1>
<lb n="0217b27"/><div1 type="pin"><mulu type="品" level="1" n="2" label="2 大心密言品"/><head>大心密言品第二</head>
<lb n="0217b28"/><lg><l>先用大心真言王</l><l>澡浴洗淨結護法</l>
<lb n="0217b29"/><l>&CB00057;水灑身加持衣</l><l>復須想念皆成就</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1089.0217c" n="0217c"/>
<lb n="0217c01"/><l>如此五種隨次第</l><l>都用大明及本印</l></lg>
<lb n="0217c02"/><p type="dharani">唵波怛摩進跢末尼摩賀惹&CB00085;<note place="inline">引</note>囉吽</p>
<lb n="0217c03"/><p>澡豆沐浴之具。各&CB00057;七遍。然後澡洗。</p>
<lb n="0217c04"/><lg><l>想水白色</l><l>猶如甘露</l><l>又<note n="0217008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">想自＝自想【甲】</note><app n="0217008"><lem>想自</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">自想</rdg></app>身</l>
<lb n="0217c05"/><l>垢穢煩惱</l><l>受此水已</l><l>一切塵勞</l>
<lb n="0217c06"/><l>皆悉<note n="0217009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔落〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0217009"><lem>落</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>盡</l><l>洗浴畢已</l><l>應須洗淨</l>
<lb n="0217c07"/><l><note n="0217010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">取＝聚&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0217010"><lem>取</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">聚</rdg></app>土少許</l><l>加持七遍</l><l>隨時洗淨</l>
<lb n="0217c08"/><l>然後著衣</l></lg>
<lb n="0217c09"/><p>時其衣亦復加持七遍作如此想。</p>
<lb n="0217c10"/><lg><l>我今此身</l><l>被金剛甲</l><l>依法<note n="0217011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">訖＝詑&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0217011"><lem>訖</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">詑</rdg></app>已</l>
<lb n="0217c11"/><l>即須灑身</l><l>用水一掬</l><l>加持七遍</l>
<lb n="0217c12"/><l>散灑其身</l><l>想虛空中</l><l>雨諸寶華</l>
<lb n="0217c13"/><l>遍滿世界</l><l><note n="0217012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">便＝使【甲】</note><app n="0217012"><lem>便</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">使</rdg></app>須護身</l><l>結此密印</l>
<lb n="0217c14"/><l>誦持七遍</l><l>印於七處</l><l>心及兩肩</l>
<lb n="0217c15"/><l>兩<note n="0217013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">眼＝胸&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0217013"><lem>眼</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">胸</rdg></app>兩膝</l><l>散於頭上</l></lg>
<lb n="0217c16"/><p><note n="0217014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">亦＝二&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0217014"><lem>亦</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">二</rdg></app>成大護身已。即須結界。</p>
<lb n="0217c17"/><lg><l>若結壇界</l><l>開於四門</l><l>不應結界</l>
<lb n="0217c18"/><l>若作結護</l><l>皆須用心</l></lg>
<lb n="0217c19"/><p>亦鋪置次第即作啟請等<note n="0217015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">事＝畢&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0217015"><lem>事</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">畢</rdg></app>。</p></div1>
<lb n="0217c20"/><div1 type="pin"><mulu type="品" level="1" n="3" label="3 根本密言品"/><head>根本密言品第三</head>
<lb n="0217c21"/><lg><l>復說根本軌儀法</l><l>想念奉請大聖王</l>
<lb n="0217c22"/><l>誦此密言及結印</l><l>一一自<note n="0217016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">想＝須【甲】</note><app n="0217016"><lem>想</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">須</rdg></app>往彼山</l>
<lb n="0217c23"/><l>存心頂禮而奉請</l><l>迎引尊者入道場</l>
<lb n="0217c24"/><l>復用遏伽而授與</l><l>香華飲食及塗<note n="0217017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">香＝身&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0217017"><lem>香</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">身</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0217c25"/><l>燈蓋幢幡兼藥等</l><l>如法供養彼明王</l>
<lb n="0217c26"/><l>想念供養尊者已</l><l>隨便持珠誦密言</l>
<lb n="0217c27"/><l>悔<note n="0217018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">先世過＝過先世【甲】</note><app n="0217018"><lem>先世過</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">過先世</rdg></app>及發願</l><l>至誠端坐觀明王</l></lg>
<lb n="0217c28"/><p>行者像前端坐思惟。存心諦觀布多勒伽山
<lb n="0217c29"/>眾寶莊嚴華果茂盛。</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1089.0218a" n="0218a"/>
<lb n="0218a01"/><lg><l>其山頂上</l><l>聖者宮殿</l><l>本在其中</l>
<lb n="0218a02"/><l>應想聖者</l><l>安坐殿中</l><l>殊妙供具</l>
<lb n="0218a03"/><l>莊嚴其身</l><l>行者於此</l><l>心想之中</l>
<lb n="0218a04"/><l>自往彼山</l><l>迎<note n="0218001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">誦＝請【甲】</note><app n="0218001"><lem>誦</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">請</rdg></app>尊者</l><l>引入道場</l>
<lb n="0218a05"/><l>於壇中心</l><l>蓮華臺上</l><l>安置聖者</l></lg>
<lb n="0218a06"/><p>次奉遏伽水。</p>
<lb n="0218a07"/><lg><l>於新銅器</l><l>或用白瓷</l><l>器盛香水</l>
<lb n="0218a08"/><l>奉於聖者</l><l>便誦真言</l><l>復想此水</l>
<lb n="0218a09"/><l>聖者受已</l><l>遍灑四方</l><l>及灑妙身</l></lg>
<lb n="0218a10"/><p>行者細觀尊灑水已。三千大千世界猶如&CB00222;
<lb n="0218a11"/>璃內外明徹中無一物。</p>
<lb n="0218a12"/><lg><l><note n="0218002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">奉＋（請）【明】</note><app n="0218002"><lem>奉</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">奉請</rdg></app>遏伽已</l><l>次復供養</l><l>香華飲食</l>
<lb n="0218a13"/><l>塗香末香</l><l>燈蓋之事</l><l>一一加持</l>
<lb n="0218a14"/><l>真言及印</l></lg>
<lb n="0218a15"/><p>供<note n="0218003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">養＋（事）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0218003"><lem>養</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">養事</rdg></app>畢已。於本尊聖者前悔謝其身<note n="0218004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">呵＝可【甲】</note><app n="0218004"><lem>呵</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">可</rdg></app>責
<lb n="0218a16"/>己過。</p>
<lb n="0218a17"/><lg><l><note n="0218005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔次〕－【甲】</note><app n="0218005"><lem>次</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>復發願</l><l>隨心所求</l><l>悉皆陳說</l>
<lb n="0218a18"/><l>於其想中</l><l>結壇三門</l><l>唯留西門</l>
<lb n="0218a19"/><l>復結大界</l><l>身外四方</l><l>周匝鋪置</l>
<lb n="0218a20"/><l>及虛空界</l><l>次用塗香</l><l>塗手臂<note n="0218006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔上〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0218006"><lem>上</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0218a21"/><l>然後<note n="0218007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">念＋（珠）【甲】</note><app n="0218007"><lem>念</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">念珠</rdg></app>誦</l></lg>
<lb n="0218a22"/><p>執念珠以<note n="0218008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">珠熏香＝珍重心【甲】</note><app n="0218008"><lem>珠熏香</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">珍重心</rdg></app>。二手合掌再三頂戴作如
<lb n="0218a23"/>是言。</p>
<lb n="0218a24"/><lg><l><note n="0218009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">我念存＝作珍重&M062403;【原】，我今存【甲】</note><note n="0218009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">我念存＝作珍重&M062403;【原】，＝我今存【甲】</note><app n="0218009"><lem>我念存</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">作珍重</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">我今存</rdg></app>心</l><l>承事聖者</l><l>持此密言</l>
<lb n="0218a25"/><l>唯願尊者</l><l>不<note n="0218010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">捨大＝捻大慈【甲】</note><app n="0218010"><lem>捨大</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">捻大慈</rdg></app>悲</l><l>莫違本誓</l>
<lb n="0218a26"/><l>發弘誓願</l><l>速現一切</l><l>妙莊嚴身</l>
<lb n="0218a27"/><l>我若見已</l><l>現身即得</l><l>證法雲地</l>
<lb n="0218a28"/><l>常侍尊者</l><l>不離左右</l><l>發此願已</l>
<lb n="0218a29"/><l>便誦根本</l><l>祕密真言曰</l></lg>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1089.0218b" n="0218b"/>
<lb n="0218b01"/><p type="dharani">曩<note place="inline">上</note>謨<note n="0218011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔引〕－【甲】＊</note><app n="0218011"><lem><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>阿<note place="inline">去引</note>囉怛曩<note place="inline">上二合</note>怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>夜<note place="inline"><note n="0218012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">長＝去&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0218012"><lem>長</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">去</rdg></app>引</note>
<lb n="0218b02"/>野<note place="inline">一</note>曩<note n="0218013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔上〕－【甲】</note><app n="0218013"><lem><note place="inline">上</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>莫阿<note place="inline">去</note>哩野<note place="inline">二合<anchor id="fxT20p0218b01"/>引</note><note n="0218014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00085;＝縛【甲】＊</note><app n="0218014"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">縛</rdg></app>路枳帝<note place="inline">三</note>濕
<lb n="0218b03"/><app type="＊" source="0218014"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>囉野<note place="inline">四</note>冒地薩怛&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>野<note place="inline">五</note>摩賀薩怛
<lb n="0218b04"/>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>野<note place="inline">六</note>摩賀迦<note place="inline">去</note>嚕抳<note place="inline">去</note>迦<note place="inline">去</note>野<note place="inline">七</note>怛&CB00135;野<note place="inline">二
<lb n="0218b05"/>合</note>他<note place="inline">去八</note>唵<note place="inline">九</note>左訖囉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00085;底<note place="inline">十</note>進跢末抳<note place="inline">去十一</note>
<lb n="0218b06"/>摩<note n="0218015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">訶＝賀【甲】</note><app n="0218015"><lem>訶</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">賀</rdg></app>跛納冥<note place="inline">二合十二</note>嚕嚕底瑟吒<note place="inline">二合十三</note>入&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>囉
<lb n="0218b07"/><note place="inline">十四</note>阿訖羅灑<note place="inline">二合</note>野<note place="inline">十五</note>吽<note place="inline">引</note>泮吒<note place="inline">十六</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合
<lb n="0218b08"/>引</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0218b09"/><p>誦此真言。於七日中滿三十萬遍。聖者即現
<lb n="0218b10"/>持誦人前。隨心所求皆得成就。</p>
<lb n="0218b11"/><lg><l>若常持<note n="0218016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">念＝誦【甲】</note><app n="0218016"><lem>念</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">誦</rdg></app></l><l>每日三時</l><l>時別念誦</l>
<lb n="0218b12"/><l>一千八遍</l><l>或<note n="0218017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">百八＝八百【甲】＊</note><app n="0218017"><lem>百八</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">八百</rdg></app>遍</l><l>如是數滿</l>
<lb n="0218b13"/><l>三十萬遍</l><l>即成悉地</l><l>時別皆作</l>
<lb n="0218b14"/><l>迎送之事</l><l>付<note n="0218018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">囑＝屬【甲】＊</note><app n="0218018"><lem>囑</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">屬</rdg></app>等法</l></lg>
<lb n="0218b15"/><p>大心密言曰。</p><p type="dharani" place="inline">唵&CB00085;<note n="0218019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">囉曩＝囉&M062403;【原】，曩【甲】</note><note n="0218019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">囉曩＝囉&M062403;【原】，＝曩【甲】</note><app n="0218019"><lem>囉曩</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">囉</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">曩</rdg></app><note place="inline">上</note>娜跛納冥<note place="inline">二合</note>進
<lb n="0218b16"/>跢末尼<note place="inline">上</note>摩賀入&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>囉吽<note place="inline">引</note>泮吒娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>
<lb n="0218b17"/>賀<note place="inline">引</note></p></div1>
<lb n="0218b18"/><div1 type="pin"><mulu type="品" level="1" n="4" label="4 小心密言品"/><head>小心密言品第四</head>
<lb n="0218b19"/><lg><l>復說最勝小心王</l><l>能成一切諸悉地</l>
<lb n="0218b20"/><l>三業齊用結妙印</l><l>誦祕真言而付<app type="＊" source="0218018"><lem>囑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">屬</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0218b21"/><l>又於想中除結界</l><l>次奉遏伽灑四方</l>
<lb n="0218b22"/><l><note n="0218020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">後＝復【甲】</note><app n="0218020"><lem>後</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">復</rdg></app>責已過<note n="0218021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">深＝除【甲】</note><app n="0218021"><lem>深</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">除</rdg></app>慚愧</l><l>引<note n="0218022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大＝入&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0218022"><lem>大</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">入</rdg></app>聖者還本宮</l>
<lb n="0218b23"/><l>安置尊者彼殿已</l><l>辭別自念還本<note n="0218023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">方＝宮【甲】</note><app n="0218023"><lem>方</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">宮</rdg></app></l></lg>
<lb n="0218b24"/><lg><l>又復行者</l><l>每持誦已</l><l>須作付<app type="＊" source="0218018"><lem>囑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">屬</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0218b25"/><l>結此密印</l><l>及誦真言</l><l>付<app type="＊" source="0218018"><lem>囑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">屬</rdg></app>聖者</l>
<lb n="0218b26"/><l>作如是語</l><l>所有遍數</l><l>及持功夫</l>
<lb n="0218b27"/><l>付<app type="＊" source="0218018"><lem>囑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">屬</rdg></app>尊者</l><l>唯願尊<note n="0218024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔者〕－【甲】＊</note><app n="0218024"><lem>者</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></l><l>受取守護</l>
<lb n="0218b28"/><l>莫令散失</l><l>又想手印</l><l>猶如寶藏</l>
<lb n="0218b29"/><l>一切遍數</l><l>安在藏中</l><l>授與聖者</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1089.0218c" n="0218c"/>
<lb n="0218c01"/><l>聖者受已</l><l>置蓮華中</l><l><note n="0218025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔作〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0218025"><lem>作</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>付<app type="＊" source="0218018"><lem>囑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">屬</rdg></app>畢</l>
<lb n="0218c02"/><l>亦須悔過</l><l>發弘誓願</l><l>然後<note n="0218026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔復〕－【甲】</note><app n="0218026"><lem>復</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>作</l>
<lb n="0218c03"/><l>聖者還宮</l><l>引送之法</l><l>即除結界</l>
<lb n="0218c04"/><l>復取香水</l><l>散灑四方</l><l>及奉聖者</l>
<lb n="0218c05"/><l>便當引送</l><l>復<note n="0218027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔結〕－【甲】</note><app n="0218027"><lem>結</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>密印</l><l><note n="0218028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔及〕－【甲】</note><app n="0218028"><lem>及</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>誦真言</l>
<lb n="0218c06"/><l>又想自身</l><l>還送聖者</l><l>至於本宮</l>
<lb n="0218c07"/><l>安置殿中</l><l>聖者坐已</l><l>自須辭去</l>
<lb n="0218c08"/><l>&CB00230;還本方</l></lg>
<lb n="0218c09"/><p>小心密言曰。</p><p type="dharani" place="inline">唵&CB00085;<note place="inline">引</note>囉娜跛納冥<note n="0218029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二合〕－【甲】</note><app n="0218029"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>吽<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0218c10"/><p>此中<note n="0218030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">密＝或【甲】</note><app n="0218030"><lem>密</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">或</rdg></app>印相貌我今說之。初作大印用種種
<lb n="0218c11"/>塗香塗於手<note n="0218031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔臂〕－【甲】</note><app n="0218031"><lem>臂</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。然後結印頂戴當心合掌。二
<lb n="0218c12"/>小指及無名指。鉤在掌中。其二頭指押中指
<lb n="0218c13"/>背第二節上。二大指並&CB00594;。</p>
<lb n="0218c14"/><lg><l>此是大心</l><l>真言密印</l><l>要須共用</l>
<lb n="0218c15"/><l>所作加持</l><l>其祕密言</l><l>各誦七遍</l>
<lb n="0218c16"/><l>各印印之</l><l>或擲或止</l><l>要當想成</l>
<lb n="0218c17"/><l>一一如法</l><l>不得就中</l><l>心緣餘境</l>
<lb n="0218c18"/><l>隨順世法</l><l>行住坐臥</l><l>安在諸佛</l>
<lb n="0218c19"/><l>甚深境界</l><l>若有行者</l><l>修此法<app type="＊" source="0218024"><lem>者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0218c20"/><l>不久即成</l><l>一切種智</l></lg>
<lb n="0218c21"/><div2 type="other"><mulu type="其他" level="2" n="1" label="第二根本真言印"/><head>第二根本真言印</head>
<lb n="0218c22"/><p>以二手腕相著。當在胸前。其十指並散。二小
<lb n="0218c23"/>指及二大指並&CB00594;猶如蓮花形。亦依前法印
<lb n="0218c24"/>之止之。惟有迎請母指來去。</p></div2>
<lb n="0218c25"/><div2 type="other"><mulu type="其他" level="2" n="2" label="第三小心真言印"/><head><note n="0218032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔第三…印〕七字－【甲】</note><app n="0218032" word-count="7"><lem>第三小心真言印</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></head>
<lb n="0218c26"/><p><note n="0218033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（印）&M062403;＋以【原】</note><app n="0218033"><lem>以</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">印以</rdg></app>二手虛心合掌猶如未開蓮花。若付<app type="＊" source="0218018"><lem>囑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">屬</rdg></app>
<lb n="0218c27"/>時依前想念。發遣尊者開二大指。此小心<note n="0218034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">密印＝印密【甲】</note><app n="0218034"><lem>密
<lb n="0218c28"/>印</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">印密</rdg></app>通蓮花部一切處用。我今於大蓮花部三
<lb n="0218c29"/>昧耶中略出<note n="0218035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此＋（法）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0218035"><lem>此</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">此法</rdg></app>祕密甚深<note n="0218036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔念誦〕－【甲】</note><app n="0218036"><lem>念誦</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>次第。其修
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1089.0219a" n="0219a"/>
<lb n="0219a01"/>行者不得錯傳如護眼目。若能如是。一切聖
<lb n="0219a02"/>者皆大歡喜憶念此人。一切善神日夜常護
<lb n="0219a03"/>不離左右。</p></div2></div1>
<lb n="0219a04"/><div1 type="pin"><mulu type="品" level="1" n="5" label="5 成就世間出世間除災護摩念誦品"/><head>成就世間出世間除災護摩念誦品第五</head>
<lb n="0219a05"/><lg><l>我今順於蓮花部</l><l>略說如意摩尼輪</l>
<lb n="0219a06"/><l>能勝諸部最祕密</l><l>成就世法出世<note n="0219001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">法＝間&M062403;【原】，門【甲】</note><note n="0219001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">法＝間&M062403;【原】，＝門【甲】</note><app n="0219001"><lem>法</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">間</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">門</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0219a07"/><l>念誦都有四種<note n="0219002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">相＝法&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0219002"><lem>相</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">法</rdg></app></l><l>行者諦聽我說之</l>
<lb n="0219a08"/><l>初作息災加持法</l><l>第二增益福智成</l>
<lb n="0219a09"/><l>第三隨心愛念法</l><l>第四降伏一切<note n="0219003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">怨＝惡&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0219003"><lem>怨</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">惡</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0219a10"/><l>此四種持<note n="0219004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">護摩事＝誦護摩&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0219004"><lem>護摩事</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">誦護摩</rdg></app></l><l>上中下法次第陳</l>
<lb n="0219a11"/><l>若欲成就息災者</l><l>先發安忍慈悲心</l>
<lb n="0219a12"/><l>須求無上妙覺地</l><l><note n="0219005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">莫＝真【甲】</note><app n="0219005"><lem>莫</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">真</rdg></app>樂聲聞二乘心</l>
<lb n="0219a13"/><l>復若<note n="0219006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">求成就＝成就求【甲】</note><app n="0219006"><lem>求成就</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">成就求</rdg></app>大事</l><l>要當先作轉障法</l>
<lb n="0219a14"/><l>又取白檀十六指</l><l>一持一燒稱<note n="0219007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">己＝所【甲】</note><app n="0219007"><lem>己</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">所</rdg></app>名</l>
<lb n="0219a15"/><l>數至<app type="＊" source="0218017"><lem>百八</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">八百</rdg></app>或千八</l><l>本所求願皆滿足</l>
<lb n="0219a16"/><l>行者若除他病時</l><l><note n="0219008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔或滅…厄〕七字－【甲】</note><app n="0219008" word-count="7"><lem>或滅國中大災厄</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0219a17"/><l>或自他災及畜生</l><l>應可存心請大聖</l>
<lb n="0219a18"/><l>於其一一大城門</l><l>想中各安本尊者</l>
<lb n="0219a19"/><l>種種殊妙寶莊嚴</l><l>思惟六臂如<note n="0219009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">盡＝畫&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0219009"><lem>盡</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">畫</rdg></app>說</l>
<lb n="0219a20"/><l>又想眉間出白光</l><l>徐徐廣引遍世界</l>
<lb n="0219a21"/><l>一切眾生所有殃</l><l>悉皆頓謝無所有</l>
<lb n="0219a22"/><l>或想此光入我身</l><l>一切罪障皆滅盡</l>
<lb n="0219a23"/><l>罪滅福生以加持</l><l>復勤念誦便成就</l></lg></div1>
<lb n="0219a24"/><div1 type="pin"><mulu type="品" level="1" n="6" label="6 增益福德品"/><head>增益福德品第六</head>
<lb n="0219a25"/><lg><l>我今略說福生法</l><l>大慈悲故順有情</l>
<lb n="0219a26"/><l>菩薩分身遍一切</l><l>隨彼眾生所樂心</l>
<lb n="0219a27"/><l>又復安立諸珍藏</l><l>種種法門各不同</l>
<lb n="0219a28"/><l>百千萬國所隨者</l><l>一一勤求皆悉成</l>
<lb n="0219a29"/><l>或說相法或無相</l><l>隨順眾生性所趣</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1089.0219b" n="0219b"/>
<lb n="0219b01"/><l>建立佛<note n="0219010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">法＝性【甲】</note><app n="0219010"><lem>法</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">性</rdg></app>護世界</l><l>大聖力勢不思議</l>
<lb n="0219b02"/><l>奉<note n="0219011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">現＝親&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0219011"><lem>現</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">親</rdg></app>一法速超越</l><l>於一法中復現三</l>
<lb n="0219b03"/><l>三部各別有三種</l><l>就中最初是攘災</l>
<lb n="0219b04"/><l>諸部攘災略說已</l><l>次當增益<note n="0219012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">今＝令【甲】</note><app n="0219012"><lem>今</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">令</rdg></app>說之</l>
<lb n="0219b05"/><l>若求長壽及財寶</l><l>復樂聰明聞持門</l>
<lb n="0219b06"/><l>或求宿命知前後</l><l>或<note n="0219013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">欣＝修【甲】</note><app n="0219013"><lem>欣</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">修</rdg></app>現世力如龍</l>
<lb n="0219b07"/><l>若為自作增益福</l><l>先須每喫三白食</l>
<lb n="0219b08"/><l>若求長壽身無患</l><l>作一火爐蓮華形</l>
<lb n="0219b09"/><l>深淺方圓皆一肘</l><l>又取五淨塗其中</l>
<lb n="0219b10"/><l>復取蘇密及<note n="0219014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">檀＝檜【甲】</note><app n="0219014"><lem>檀</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">檜</rdg></app>木</l><l>一&CB00057;一燒稱己名</l>
<lb n="0219b11"/><l>數至<app type="＊" source="0218017"><lem>百八</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">八百</rdg></app>一千八</l><l>乃至三千隨<note n="0219015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">前＝所【甲】</note><app n="0219015"><lem>前</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">所</rdg></app>儀</l>
<lb n="0219b12"/><l>若有先世極重業</l><l>不過萬遍悉皆除</l>
<lb n="0219b13"/><l>除滅罪已增<note n="0219016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">福＝益&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0219016"><lem>福</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">益</rdg></app>智</l><l>即得無病及命長</l>
<lb n="0219b14"/><l>若為他故作此事</l><l>但稱彼名法則同</l>
<lb n="0219b15"/><l>行者如法作存心</l><l>每日<note n="0219017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">晨朝＝辰時&M062403;【原】，晨時【甲】</note><note n="0219017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">晨朝＝辰時&M062403;【原】，＝晨時【甲】</note><app n="0219017"><lem>晨朝</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">辰時</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">晨時</rdg></app>取柳木</l>
<lb n="0219b16"/><l>&CB00057;滿八百<note n="0219018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">便＝使&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0219018"><lem>便</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">使</rdg></app>嚼之</l><l>不久一月或三月</l>
<lb n="0219b17"/><l>即能開心得聰明</l><l>作護摩用小心&CB00057;</l>
<lb n="0219b18"/><l>念誦根本大真言</l><l>我此略說增益福</l>
<lb n="0219b19"/><l>無福眾生速加持</l><l>莫<note n="0219019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">論＝福&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0219019"><lem>論</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">福</rdg></app>作此數種法</l>
<lb n="0219b20"/><l>但願長<note n="0219020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">命＝念【甲】</note><app n="0219020"><lem>命</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">念</rdg></app>大護身</l><l>若能每日持千八</l>
<lb n="0219b21"/><l>現世即得宿命通</l><l>日夜殷勤&M010527;修<note n="0219021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">習＝集【甲】＊</note><app n="0219021"><lem>習</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">集</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0219b22"/><l>所求悉地無不成</l><l>又若服藥求色力</l>
<lb n="0219b23"/><l>根本真言加持之</l><l>念誦十萬滿足已</l>
<lb n="0219b24"/><l><note n="0219022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔每須…之〕七字－【甲】</note><app n="0219022" word-count="7"><lem>每須空服取服之</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></l><l>三七五七復過七</l>
<lb n="0219b25"/><l>力同九龍等無差</l><l>若持延年甘露藥</l>
<lb n="0219b26"/><l>或得一劫過<note n="0219023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">中劫＝劫中&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0219023"><lem>中劫</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">劫中</rdg></app></l><l>若持藥草求成就</l>
<lb n="0219b27"/><l>過於諸部以得成</l><l>牛酥雌黃雄黃等</l>
<lb n="0219b28"/><l><note n="0219024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">須＝顆&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0219024"><lem>須</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">顆</rdg></app>持一物置壇中</l><l>白月一日或十五</l>
<lb n="0219b29"/><l>初夜起首念誦之</l><l>一期持誦勿間斷</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1089.0219c" n="0219c"/>
<lb n="0219c01"/><l>及現三相唯限之</l><l>初現煖相成聰智</l>
<lb n="0219c02"/><l>第二煙相隱其軀</l><l>第三火現昇空去</l>
<lb n="0219c03"/><l>此得成就大仙人</l><l>悉地牛酥應當服</l>
<lb n="0219c04"/><l>雄黃等藥用塗之</l><l>我今說此增益訖</l>
<lb n="0219c05"/><l>行者努力守護之</l></lg></div1>
<lb n="0219c06"/><div1 type="pin"><mulu type="品" level="1" n="7" label="7 隨心憶念品"/><head>隨心憶念品第七</head>
<lb n="0219c07"/><lg><l>我今復說隨順<note n="0219025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">事＝等&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0219025"><lem>事</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">等</rdg></app></l><l>人與非人及畜生</l>
<lb n="0219c08"/><l>又取鹽和大麥<note n="0219026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB03475;＝麵【甲】＊</note><app n="0219026"><lem>&CB03475;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">麵</rdg></app></l><l>所求隨心作其形</l>
<lb n="0219c09"/><l>男左女右從&CB00560;興</l><l>須用<note n="0219027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔賓〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0219027"><lem>賓</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>鐵刀細<note n="0219028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">截＋（之）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0219028"><lem>截</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">截之</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0219c10"/><l>每日三時各百八</l><l>乃至千八自隨心</l>
<lb n="0219c11"/><l>若欲羅遮令憶念</l><l>所造形持稱彼名</l>
<lb n="0219c12"/><l>護摩亦須念名號</l><l>不過八百即隨心</l>
<lb n="0219c13"/><l>若攝諸龍作隨順</l><l>先作一龍似蛇形</l>
<lb n="0219c14"/><l>若欲<note n="0219029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">祈＝期【甲】</note><app n="0219029"><lem>祈</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">期</rdg></app>雨須青色</l><l>復若澇時應赤色</l>
<lb n="0219c15"/><l>燒火須用乳汁木</l><l>不過三日即<note n="0219030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">成＝滅【甲】</note><app n="0219030"><lem>成</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">滅</rdg></app>之</l>
<lb n="0219c16"/><l>作法<note n="0219031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">應＝亦【甲】</note><app n="0219031"><lem>應</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">亦</rdg></app>須至誠意</l><l>就中不得<note n="0219032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">懈＝晡【甲】</note><app n="0219032"><lem>懈</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">晡</rdg></app>慢心</l>
<lb n="0219c17"/><l>若攝諸天藥叉等</l><l>隨類各各稱本名</l>
<lb n="0219c18"/><l>若有怨家令歡喜</l><l>念誦亦得轉彼心</l>
<lb n="0219c19"/><l>或作護摩或持誦</l><l>上中下品<note n="0219033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">怨家別＝再處之【甲】</note><app n="0219033"><lem>怨家別</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">再處之</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0219c20"/><l>上根福<note n="0219034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">報＝能【甲】</note><app n="0219034"><lem>報</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">能</rdg></app>三百遍</l><l>中下無福再稱之</l>
<lb n="0219c21"/><l>隨心念誦我略說</l><l>智者應須諦思惟</l>
<lb n="0219c22"/><l>一切部中總攝盡</l><l>祕密最<note n="0219035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">要＝處【甲】</note><app n="0219035"><lem>要</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">處</rdg></app>蓮華心</l></lg></div1>
<lb n="0219c23"/><div1 type="pin"><mulu type="品" level="1" n="8" label="8 阿毘遮嚕迦品"/><head>阿毘遮嚕迦品第八</head>
<lb n="0219c24"/><lg><l>我今稽首彼大聖</l><l>為現種種方便門</l>
<lb n="0219c25"/><l>護佛法故現忿怒</l><l>降伏破滅聖法人</l>
<lb n="0219c26"/><l>此中火爐須三角</l><l>用燒雌木兼<note n="0219036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">濕＝溫【甲】＊</note><app n="0219036"><lem>濕</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">溫</rdg></app>薪</l>
<lb n="0219c27"/><l>若作此法須黑月</l><l>或用一日及月頭</l>
<lb n="0219c28"/><l><note n="0219037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">露＝路【甲】</note><app n="0219037"><lem>露</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">路</rdg></app>體<note n="0219038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">樂幽＝叩齒&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0219038" corr="叩齒" resp="【原】">樂幽</sic>及忿怒</l><l>大聲持誦稱彼名</l>
<lb n="0219c29"/><l>惡酥惡油擲爐<note n="0219039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">底＝舌&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0219039"><lem>底</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">舌</rdg></app></l><l>不滿千八自然成</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1089.0220a" n="0220a"/>
<lb n="0220a01"/><l>降伏鬼神卒暴者</l><l>應可復燒禮<note n="0220001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嚕＝唱【甲】</note><app n="0220001"><lem>嚕</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">唱</rdg></app>根</l>
<lb n="0220a02"/><l>或燒苦楝或生木</l><l><app type="＊" source="0219026"><lem>&CB03475;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">麵</rdg></app>和人血復作形</l>
<lb n="0220a03"/><l>一截一&CB00057;百八遍</l><l>不過三<note n="0220002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">日＝百【甲】</note><app n="0220002"><lem>日</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">百</rdg></app>即調柔</l>
<lb n="0220a04"/><l>若復降伏滅法者</l><l>加意供養<note n="0220003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大＝本【甲】</note><app n="0220003"><lem>大</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">本</rdg></app>明王</l>
<lb n="0220a05"/><l>用諸毒藥燒爐<note n="0220004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">中＝&M034294;【甲】</note><app n="0220004"><lem>中</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&M034294;</rdg></app></l><l>又取<app type="＊" source="0219036"><lem>濕</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">溫</rdg></app>薪作護摩</l>
<lb n="0220a06"/><l>於三日中八百遍</l><l>令彼惡人即迴心</l>
<lb n="0220a07"/><l><note n="0220005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">復＝彼【甲】</note><app n="0220005"><lem>復</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">彼</rdg></app>若不作護摩事</l><l>持誦根本真言明</l>
<lb n="0220a08"/><l>所欲降伏一切者</l><l>句句皆須稱彼名</l>
<lb n="0220a09"/><l>其數復滿八百遍</l><l>彼即自來尊敬之</l>
<lb n="0220a10"/><l>依法略說此調伏</l><l>行者應須諦思惟</l>
<lb n="0220a11"/><l>甚深祕密口<note n="0220006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">訣＝決【甲】</note><app n="0220006"><lem>訣</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">決</rdg></app>法</l><l>次第念誦都攝門</l>
<lb n="0220a12"/><l>若能承<note n="0220007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">侍＝傳&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0220007"><lem>侍</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">傳</rdg></app>此尊者</l><l>不是一生種善根</l>
<lb n="0220a13"/><l>曾經無量諸佛所</l><l>修<app type="＊" source="0219021"><lem>習</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">集</rdg></app>菩<note n="0220008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">提＝薩【甲】</note><app n="0220008"><lem>提</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">薩</rdg></app>究竟門</l>
<lb n="0220a14"/><l>就中若值善知識</l><l>一生即入不壞門</l>
<lb n="0220a15"/><l>我若廣說此功德</l><l>無量億劫<note n="0220009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">歎＝莫【甲】</note><app n="0220009"><lem>歎</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">莫</rdg></app>無窮</l>
<lb n="0220a16"/><l>今已略陳此少耳</l><l>行者精心勤修之</l></lg>
<lb n="0220a17"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead>都表如意輪儀軌</jhead></juan></div1>
